  <h2 id="n5-n4">Beginner: N5 to N4 (Months 1-12)</h2>

  <p>The beginner phase is where you build the foundation that everything else rests on. This is where consistent study habits matter most.</p>

  <p><strong>N5 Level (3-6 months at 1-2 hours/day):</strong></p>

